value.0: Hyper and playful, Claisi excitedly meets anyone who comes to visit the little den.
Tall and strong, Faith is the youngest of the breeding females. She watches over her pups with a dangerously protective stance.
This young pup seems to have developed a constant itch just above his eye.
A sloppy, wet tongue lolls out of Jediun's mouth as he almost constantly hounds the other wolves for food.
This little fellow is resting. Probably recovering from some injury or another.

A fine stringed instrument, a lute is very mobile, and as such, a favorite of traveling minstrels everywhere.  It has a pleasing sound, as the strings musical vibrations echo in the hollow wooden chamber and reverberate.

These squirrels are fast, twitchy, focused and unusually organized for squirrels, watching every one with their beady eyes, as if they are the most powerful guards in existence. It's a save bet there are a lot more of them around that you don't see.
